  "text": "For each gauge, we can calculate the propagators from the gauge fixed action eq. (39) in a similar way for the n = 1 open string field theory case [CITATION_1] . Note also that the action given in eq.(39) is invariant under the BRST and the anti-BRST transformations δ B andδ B satisfying the condition",
